{"tid":1467142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家冷靜啲睇下 依家連登似啲咩","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:31.000Z","uid":97941,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e729e88ef20d6707a40046fd41610ed9abaa7359","tid":1467142,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xft3hKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxft3hKk.png&h=dab1e613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好再屌<br />\n冷靜啲傾下<br />\n運動未完<br />\n今日只係成場運動其中一點<br />\n係會有手尾跟<br />\n但唔好無限放大今日嘅事<br />\n抗爭嘅路仲有排行<br />\n大家理性啲檢討<br />\n聽日仲要繼續上路"},{"pid":"67e6f13665f7432953924ccd5ff17d1ecf48a445","tid":1467142,"uid":203619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"我只推 正常POST<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/RfNfTgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfNfTgW.png&h=52691539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我今日留意到警察係機場用槍指嚇市民<br />\n你呢?"},{"pid":"3d5b9e799efb29ecb2a9644635beaf64dfa74d2e","tid":1467142,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得要有行動共識, 行動守則, 現場討論又好, 事前討論又好<br />\n個個守住幾條行動鐵規, 其他事就自由發揮, <br />\n就例如, 唔打/唔會誤傷到FA+記者, 讓路比救護消防"},{"pid":"f0467dbbfb2a8abf8a2c266a9afffa41ba783c9b","tid":1467142,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123a5528cd6e40081948fb6910813f47cea5184a","tid":1467142,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09af9b3192bc76b666d0857f96dc3637a25c909","tid":1467142,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:01.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲呀大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06b881ea79745c19028b34ce2283f03e3aea0f3","tid":1467142,"uid":27557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"機場既同我入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDDRRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDDRRS</a><br />\n<br />\n未賽後都要檢討 跪求大家睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDQeRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDQeRS</a>"},{"pid":"b6457055eee6dd58d53d2f9e404daec971f022ed","tid":1467142,"uid":141328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:22.000Z","msg":"既然行錯左,我地要認!!!!!!<br />\n唔係割席,但我地今次的確係錯左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地要係記者會同文宣提及我地做錯左<br />\n但同時,我地都要表明!!就算我地有同顆可能做錯,我地都唔割席,為佢地道歉<br />\n<br />\n要緊記既係,我地可能做左啲不可挽回既事,但係我地同班警犬係有分別!!!!!!!!!<br />\n我地係會反思做錯左啲咩,會改進,會認錯<br />\n我地要一個國際級既道歉!!!!!!!<br />\n就算啲人以後針住呢件事黎講,我地仲可以名正言順咁話我地係有羞恥之心,同某啲動物係唔同<br />\n呢個就係我地幫到前線既方法!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以因為一次錯就放棄今次行動!!!! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277e1a758065fa3421fc476116d255bfeab3aa8d","tid":1467142,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"我地嚟緊仲有818<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6391623a4c8ec810a5211c8f498724c6e2fa14ee","tid":1467142,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">團結就是力量</span></span>"},{"pid":"d9cf305af759caa849fc8d6ef9941092f545d808","tid":1467142,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔好再傳失敗論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5efa2a0a32950c4e4cdac8331f8996d4353a0f","tid":1467142,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"有嘢做得唔好檢討完再改<br />\n屌嚟屌去冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792e1c8162e6c04565c8c97135891756fcf53ff4","tid":1467142,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}